		"description": "<p dir=\"ltr\">With a whoop and a smile you celebrate overwhelming success!</p><p dir=\"ltr\">When a creature within range succeeds at a skill check or saving throw with a DC of 13 or higher, or critically succeeds on any attack roll, you can cast this spell as a reaction. When you do so, the target gains 12 temporary hit points and advantage on persuasion checks for 10 minutes.</p><p dir=\"ltr\"><strong id=\"docs-internal-guid-32da0f37-7fff-9df5-b562-b5a89a212e4e\">Cast at Higher Levels.</strong> When cast at higher levels, the DC required increases by 1, and the target gains an additional 6 temporary hit points, for each spell slot level above 1st.</p>",
